## Practical 6 â€“ Softmax Regression for Multiclass Classification

This practical implements softmax regression for multiclass classification from first principles, including training via gradient descent and detailed performance evaluation.

### Key tasks
- Implement softmax regression with numerical stability
- Optimise model parameters using gradient descent
- Predict class labels using maximum class probability
- Evaluate performance using accuracy, confusion matrix, precision, and recall

